Stir together flour, baking powder and salt. Set aside. In large mixing bowl, combine Kellogg's(R) All-Bran(R) cereal, sugar, milk, orange juice and peel. Let stand about 2 minutes or until cereal softens. Add egg and oil. Beat well. Stir in almonds. Add flour mixture, stirring only until combined. Portion evenly into twelve 2 1/2-inch muffin-pan cups coated with cooking spray. Bake at 400 degrees F about 20 minutes or until lightly browned. Serve warm.